wrt%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E6%89%A9%E5%AE%B9"><span class="toc-number">3.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">openwrt系统扩容</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%89%A9%E5%AE%B9%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%AD%A5"><span class="toc-number">3.3.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">扩容第一步</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-4"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E6%89%A9%E5%AE%B9%E5%90%8E%E7%BB%AD"><span class="toc-number">3.3.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">扩容后续</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#mentoHUST%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91%E5%8F%8A%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85"><span class="toc-number">4.</span> <span class="toc-text">mentoHUST插件编译及其安装</span></a><ol class="toc-child"><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#mentoHUST%E6%8F%92%E4%BB%B6%E7%BC%96%E8%AF%91"><span class="toc-number">4.1.</span> <span class="toc-text">mentoHUST插件编译</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#mentoHUST%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85"><span class="toc-number">4.2.</span> <span class="toc-text">mentoHUST安装</span></a></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-3"><a class="toc-link" href="#mentoHUST%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8"><span class="toc-number">4.3.</span> <span class="toc-text">mentoHUST使用</span></a></li></ol></li><li class="toc-item toc-level-2"><a class="toc-link" href="#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87ssh%E8%BF%9E%E6%8E%A5%E8%87%B3J1900%E8%B7%AF%E7%94%B1%E5%99%A8"><span class="toc-number">5.</span> <span class="toc-text">通过ssh连接至J1900路由器</span></a></li></ol></div></div><div class="card-widget card-recent-post"><div class="item-headline"><i class="fas fa-history"></i><span>最新文章</span></div><div class="aside-list"><div class="aside-list-item no-cover"><div class="content"><a class="title" href="/2023/12/01/codetop100note" title="codetop 100题（暂定） 思路笔记">codetop 100题（暂定） 思路笔记</a><time datetime="2023-12-01T07:55:45.000Z" title="发表于 2023-12-01 15:55:45">2023-12-01</time></div